  <h2>Sensitivity Analysis</h2>
  <p>Our base case uses a {(growthRatePhase1 * 100).toFixed(0)}% growth rate and a {(discountRate * 100).toFixed(0)}% discount rate. Here's what the intrinsic value looks like under different assumptions.</p>

